			<h2>This is a great product</h2>
			<p>This is my second Weber gas grill. When you assemble a Weber, the dedication to engineering is evident. Clear instructions, strong fasteners, and no fuss. The holes all line up perfectly and items like shelves hang on the frame to allow you to fasten without gravity being a problem and requiring 2 people. In the rare instance you need parts, they are available and fit perfectly with no hassle.</p>
