			<h2>Will never buy again</h2>
			<p>I've owned many grills over my life and am nearing retirement age. I wish that I had purchased this Weber grill at least (4) grills ago and would have saved money in the long run. I have also assembled many cheaper grills that were not Weber. In this Weber grill, the parts fit like they were finely tooled to very exacting tolerances. I've really never seen anything like it, and I also understood why a Weber costs more (up-front) than cheaper gas grills. It costs to make a grill as good as a Weber and the engineering is something to behold as you assemble one.</p>
