			<h2>So close but not quite</h2>
			<p>Once I got it up and running I fired it up and it worked BEAUTIFULLY. I'm super happy with it and have had it now for about 2 weeks - I have been grilling pretty much every day, sometimes more than once a day HAHA. I love it!! it's by far the best grill I have ever had, and the flavor is exceptional. This was something I was afraid I would lose with going to a gas grill, but with the cast iron grates and flavorizer bars, I honestly can't tell much of a difference from charcoal grilling. Overall I am extremely happy with my purchase and I would definitely recommend this grill to anyone who doesn't mind paying a little extra to get a great product. The cooking is consistant, the gas is much easier than charcoal, the grill preheats within 10 minutes, and the clean up is relatively easy as well. Oh - by the way, I am IN LOVE with my grill.... did I say that already? LOL :)</p>
