				<div class="star-off"><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></div>
			</div>
			<h2>It breaks immediately</h2>
			<p>This grill is amazing, and i use it year round regardless of temperature. Ive used it in -20 to over 100 degrees and it worked like a champ. Every area of the grill cooks equally even and just performs so well. The sear station is great for when im cooking steaks and i can get them great sear marks. I have also added the front handle light which is wonderful at night. I bought the weber hand tools which go great with the 6 tool hooks on the grills resting arms. Ive used this grill in the rain and snow and it hasn't rusted. This grill is a piece of art and is built so well and looks gorgous sitting on my porch. I had no issues putting the grill together and it always fires up perfect each time. Weber also has great customer service when ive called for questions regarding models and what not. I also had a weber kettle shipped to me some time ago from a retail store and the lid was dented (not webers fault) and i called weber to ask how i would go about getting another hood. Weber apologized and asked for my address. The next morning UPS knocked on my door with a brand new in the box hood that was flawless. Rest easy that you get great service and great quality from Weber.</p>
